Electronic trigger control Burst mode for 4 or 8 rounds at a time! Tactical foregrip Weaver/Picatinny rails Adjustable front sight Adjustable rear sight Built-in (non-removable) mag If you use the bulk-fill CO2 adapter, the buttstock won’t fit on the gun The Umarex EBOS is one of the most exciting CO2 guns made. We’ve taken the basic gun and kicked it up a couple notches by making an adapter that attaches to a bulk-fill CO2 tank. The adapter is listed in the ACCESSORIES link for this gun. It’s a simple process. As it comes from the factory, the EBOS CO2 submachine gun can use only 88-gram CO2 tanks. They will deliver a lot of shots. UMAREX BULK FILL ADAPTER (I believe this was made by JimC for DrozdMax) Enables the use of refillable paintball tanks. More shooting before needing to refill. NOTE: The paintball tank valve will immediately open when it’s completely screwed into the adapter. Make sure the adapter is tightly/securely installed in the gun before the tank is tightened down.
